{"arkId":"cl010112814","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112814","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Aigui\u00e8re-casque","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Aigui\u00e8re-casque"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1700 - 1800","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 518 - Sauvageot, Vitrine 3C","room":"Salle 518, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11997","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"verrerie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"L\u0027aigui\u00e8re en verre incolore souffl\u00e9 et travaill\u00e9 \u00e0 la pince, \u00e0 la silhouette cylindrique, est munie d\u0027une anse arrondie, fa\u00e7onn\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u0027aide d\u0027un \u00e9pais filet plat appliqu\u00e9 sur la panse par deux points d\u0027attache. Ce filet s\u0027enroule sur lui-m\u00eame aux deux extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s, formant ainsi poussoir \u00e0 la partie haute. Le bec a \u00e9t\u00e9 obtenu par pincement de la paraison encore molle. L\u0027emplacement du bec a \u00e9t\u00e9 enrichi, \u00e0 l\u0027ext\u00e9rieur, d\u0027une grosse larme de verre stri\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u0027aide d\u0027une pince. La partie sup\u00e9rieure de la panse est retourn\u00e9e vers l\u0027ext\u00e9rieur, formant un \u00e9pais ourlet. La jambe creuse qui relie l\u0027aigui\u00e8re au pied pr\u00e9sente la forme d\u0027un entonnoir \u00e0 ressaut. Le pi\u00e9douche, circulaire et creux, est termin\u00e9 par un rebord \u00e9pais repli\u00e9 par-dessus.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"22","displayDimension":"22 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"20","displayDimension":"20 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"13","displayDimension":"13 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : verre\r\nTechnique : souffl\u00e9 (techniques verre\/vitrail\/plastique)","placeOfCreation":"Normandie (Europe-\u003EFrance) (?) ; Orl\u00e9ans (Centre-\u003ELoiret) (?)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"Normandie (Europe-\u003EFrance) (Provient d\u0027un ch\u00e2teau normand)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Provient d\u0027un ch\u00e2teau normand ; acquis dans le commerce d\u0027art, 2002","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"26\/09\/2002","startYear":2002,"endYear":2002},{"type":"date du conseil artistique des mus\u00e9es nationaux","value":"02\/10\/2002","startYear":2002,"endYear":2002},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9","value":"14\/10\/2002","startYear":2002,"endYear":2002}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"place":[{"value":"Orl\u00e9ans"},{"value":"Normandie"}],"objectType":[{"value":"verrerie"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Alcouffe, Daniel ; Baratte, Sophie ; Coquery, Emmanuel ; Dion, Anne ; Durand, Jannic ; Gaborit-Chopin, Danielle ; Mabille, G\u0